            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, combine your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix</strong> with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>rice vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and <strong>salt </strong>and mix it all together – this is your<strong> quick-pickled slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1691060761992-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1691060761992-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
