    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Malaysian-style fried chicken</strong> with the <strong>coconut rice</strong> and <strong>quick-pickled slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Serve the <strong>chilli tamarind sauce</strong> to the side for dipping</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
